 de Gernon of Grimston Hall, avait 19 ans et sa mère, Mary Potton or Potkin, avait 20 ans. Il a épousé Alice de Odyngseles environ 1355, à Cavendish, Suffolk, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Ils ont eu au moins 2 fils. En 1372, sa profession de son indiquée est chief justice of the king's bench à Angleterre. Il est décédé le 15 juin 1381, dans sa ville natale, et a été enterré à Bury St Edmunds, Suffolk, Angleterre."},"de":{"before 1340–15 June 1381":"vor 1340–15. Juni 1381","1340–1381":"1340–1381","1330–1381":"1330–1381","1358–1396":"1358–1396","1374–1406":"1374–1406","1374–1417":"1374–1417","1320–Male":"1320–Verstorben","1319–Female":"1319–Verstorben","15 June 1381":"15. Juni 1381","1374":"1374","1396":"1396","1330":"1330","1340":"1340","1372":"1372","1371":"1371","1381":"1381","1358":"1358","about 1358":"um 1358","1320":"1320","before 1340":"vor 1340","about 1355":"um 1355","1319":"1319","1417":"1417","1406":"1406","England":"England","of Cavendish Overhall, Suffolk, England ":"Cavendish, Suffolk, England, United Kingdom","Devendish, Overhall, Suffolk, England":"Suffolk, England, United Kingdom","Bury St Edmunds, Suffolk, England":"Bury St Edmunds, Suffolk, England","Cavendish, Suffolk, England":"Cavendish, Suffolk, England","lifeSummary":"Als Sir John Cavendish vor 1340 in Cavendish, Suffolk, England geboren wurde, war sein Vater Robert de Gernon of Grimston Hall 19 und seine Mutter Mary Potton or Potkin 20. Er hat um 1355 in Cavendish, Suffolk, England, United Kingdom Alice de Odyngseles geheiratet. Sie hatten mindestens 2 Söhne. 1372 ist sein Beruf als chief justice of the king's bench in England aufgeführt. Er starb am 15. Juni 1381 in seinem Geburtsort und wurde in Bury St Edmunds, Suffolk, England begraben."},"ht":{"before 1340–15 June 1381":"before 1340–15 June 1381","1340–1381":"1340–1381","1330–1381":"1330–1381","1358–1396":"1358–1396","1374–1406":"1374–1406","1374–1417":"1374–1417","1320–Male":"1320–Desede","1319–Female":"1319–Desede","15 June 1381":"15 June 1